SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777359931
OL,3,CQuizzer 'had to have cuppa' after
OL,4,Cwinning Who Wants To Be A Millionaire?
OL,6,FThe most recent was Donald Fear in
OL,7,F2020, who answered all 15 questions
OL,8,Fcorrectly with three lifelines
OL,9,Fremaining.
OL,11,FThe other winners are: Judith Keppel
OL,12,F(2000), David Edwards (2001), Robert
OL,13,FBrydges (2001), Pat Gibson (2004) and
OL,14,FIngram Wilcox (2006).
OL,16,FListen to the ITV News entertainment
OL,17,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
